 style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>打游擊戰去搵該區既建制派議員</strong></span></span>同佢地開party一齊賀一賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，至於邊一區去邊間就大家自己衡量下喇﹗<br />\n<br />\n屯門區區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=1225c012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n荃灣區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=e7ece826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n沙田區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=61f718d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n黃大仙區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=e5c7a063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%83%E5%A4%A7%E4%BB%99%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n深水埗區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=1cd7334b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n灣仔區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583&d=Cf%2FvPHDuk0dzuxx%2BuF7CdajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=a236c283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話（呢個係每日都可以做既）</span></span></strong><br />\n打電話搵議員(之前有巴打post過出黎，可以自己搵下)問下國慶期間區內有咩最新活動、巴士路線、有咩醫生診所好介紹呀等等，電話打唔通既whatsapp都可以，無whatsapp既巴絲打可以send email去，連email都無既可以fax過去查詢下，無人應既話可以搵下無限fax大法fax到佢應機為止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2.連儂牆</strong></span></span><br />\n都係搵立法會議員/區議員辦事處啦，無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3.裝修</strong></span></span><br />\n有好多議員都扎根起屋邨做左好耐，裡面啲裝修又殘又舊，有心既手足可以襯國慶幫佢地補下油、翻新下添置返少少國慶節日既氣氛，用咩色就自己決定啦。<br />\n補充:好多office既出入口好窄，大家入office查詢既時候動作唔好太大呀，唔小心撞到佢地d玻璃就大鑊喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>4.餵office既龜龜食野(蟲系魔法師出動)</strong></span></span><br />\n巴絲打們都可以準備少少紅蟲、蚯蚓、生雞蛋、甜野呀個d比入面既龜龜食，可以吸引到更多蟲蟲輕易大量繁殖既就更好。大家知啦，議員們公事繁忙，萬一無時間餵佢地，龜龜都仲有少少野食丫嘛。<br />\n補充：拉開櫃桶餵既時候記住小心啲，唔好倒瀉手上罐可樂呀，會惹到成地蟻架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>原post:</strong></span><br />\n國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a>"},{"pid":"bcef5a450ecef1bd2d0cac2530be75905490d89a","tid":1607534,"uid":142429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:04:25.000Z","msg":"又跟民權抗爭老將的法國朋友聊天，當然論及香港的反送中運動，朋友說，看到香港警察一身造價不菲的裝備，頭部更用非常堅固的頭盔完全包裹，鐵甲人一樣，非常安全，但他說，非常奇怪，香港的抗爭者竟然不會向這些防暴警頭盔的保護鏡投擲任何<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">顏料</span></strong>，個個防暴警的頭盔保護鏡竟然一塵不染。他說，投擲顏料相當容易，而保護鏡一旦看不清，就要把保護鏡拉起，甚至要卸下頭盔，自衛能力就大減，或要以真面目示人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Party差你一個炸 帶啲野黎啦</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"50f5fae7e12f96856ebe813c111da3064291d461","tid":1607534,"uid":224657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n我姑丈做派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比佢個女篤灰<br />\n油塘揸去南昌再落尖沙咀"},{"pid":"9e8ed53a7ab52557388f3a5e6f75eab843da659a","tid":1607534,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:05:12.000Z","msg":"呢個時候仲諗住玩正常程序，政府會公平執法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca1d5978be786d0d9d686b696218b98d77376f5","tid":1607534,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:06:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要影埋車牌同旗一張相過就最好</span></span>"},{"pid":"8b4eda54651f4f1ec68a9dde97c1e470600aea4e","tid":1607534,"uid":24139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:07:03.000Z","msg":"有，係龍翔道快速駛過，但十幾架之間都係見到一架啫，鬼唔望佢成架車被人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf28e09fa75cbf2a4c709b1916966b35b090818d","tid":1607534,"uid":182774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T02:09:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7260a1a4bdb4efbff94fcb10578fbbef3eee8a29","tid":1607534,"uid":7